                    <span>I originally got this book while looking for reverse psychology techniques, and most of the secrets in this book work on almost anyone. Includes ways to make a great first impression, get anyone to like you, get the upper hand in an arguement, catch someone in a lie, get anyone to do a favor for you plus lots more! Some of the techniques I would classify as reverse psychology. This book is an invaluable addition to my library!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Powerfull</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
